discounting + no_discounting_future_humans + animals_matter_a_lot + suffering_focused + living_in_simulation&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;If most observers like us are simulated, the astronomical future that justified x-risk work probably gets switched off long before it happens. The same expected-value reasoning that bought astronomical stakes now attenuates them: future-facing value is multiplied by the probability the simulation keeps running, and the ranking slides back toward the present. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 3 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 4 no_discounting_future_humans → 5 animals_matter_a_lot → 6 suffering_focused → 9 living_in_simulation" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJylVmFTIjkQ%2FStd1l0dcooDqHtwxQdEXK1lby3kbutKrDHM9DA5M8lUknFkXf%2F7dWZAQGDPquOLY7rzuvt1%2BiXPeyFGLBO2p0Lca%2B8dHUGn04GRZlyCVRBo9m1GH7mEcdbw6seQKy3CR4455HW%2F4Tf9Y%2F%2FEP%2FVbUDFWpdDadwBjSUBdY7IktVxJCGLCa4MHKdMqiDkTDq7eakAdIqZ9lrOZH2cJk2ZhaACTPGHC%2BEYlmMfMLixNiDKbaZxv8BNmLWo%2F5zb2Q24ClUnL5XThfgxSra77a7sXXiev4eZwzBfqNeQpmCyKUBfbVZAZDBemFgj%2B6Na59A1PMsFcxQUBfRbEwJYscAMMrmc2pu%2BICwTieGk2R2BdlSwMzQFopMZwiQaULsA0HhJ5LEFKjhtatzGWvP5iiBAZFBi%2FQ6CSVBlX%2F6sD7ZUhEiItcVOgGctkyISSCAl1XtTg%2FrWx%2Fcd7l6rbjk8pBpY2PjKRIaioQFiegVoBdobGwiSbQebCuI0GVwtrw02seZLCVxTUbYRrrf4h3HL3x%2F4f%2FWF31D%2BHyQymKFEzi7V0tjhwGHK7RlOVjAfUVFsm45gkpALrnGvCBaRe0R%2BiGV0LlJ4SRymlwPQMJhQi4gGn7wM46198GfaJA81EgZAjn8bumBAjQrkRiPl92TmhplJpOiPQ8n6G3hVUlKZ6D1V0mLCp5DYLEc6%2BjPq9fcrHqCz9xG0QozxnYnaN%2Bk8TQgeexxIgRZUKvESRYvhq8WreiQvo1U6cT45CTJAy%2BUgtdBCli1cvfby6cyoONeqIBTZj4ozJh7%2BKTjnX5o5I1S3QVajU4XAX3P5YvozlNFwrxOXiHc%2BT8RpjyZJow6E5r8hrULqMJxsOi2oaVLONxZq9Xms46%2FEHYjNP100Nz3O2D8eUxFjmXISTbGrWfU5Ln98ahQ8TIsJwSy%2B6U80DksCMzkCPWWasVmmM5NVDSasL4pvzVIvu0NCjuWGPBavnSgimr6KV3eWeIv%2BG8w%2FLuAMeOVPTKyL3SDkE%2F1YoRl%2BGriEEKzdgFueiaDlN%2F8NNTGM0xEStxncl42G9qJk%2BvJbzLsXOVW269sayBwdZ95a%2Fwtt783snL9X%2FpqG6Vvmv70N9DzHVHxBR3VJ2cYRJA3OlthyCpyGBDTHMgk1Cm3NC643%2FR%2Bj2GDtzLa%2BQ2%2Fy8O%2FgbiGHtdDglff3prr2qa%2BGa5lmezO%2BGpaYFioykeMTvG%2F2m7ezNLQ1pZo2TTu70mW5Nd2904NZV8Aw05NiG8d5ABaSDTuPgoRS58d4B5OErsW1IkMnKVhXcp6JJnuDlYB3U9bhUcDHbDrcqQT9CoYtGgHuOUEma2xlUup8v9rdjrsmWA92E7F59hiPozbH60mpM6U7FTJuYpztgV8VuV64j6tOle4cgDJBNM9yOtSaMJVardbqBtv2W3dGYVUEtIb3WZoJfSVjpmWIIx0AlLlNN6b6n4xSi2UHpphzPI2yhdjC46J%2FvoPCNYu8GuQLDInR9HpYTDkN6gzAdxDsy3BCCNew7N32abj%2F3jOrAgBtb00gjaLBS%2FGOUtmezSjkdB%2FD8%2Fek7PNVWwrzs0505ce%2BiDsyBbr27%2BVCPtr6sRpdXN8vJbEPx5OVE%2B2TxvKKZ55SFoblceaxRBOexGn0s917%2BBZgKBug%3D" id="w1_2_3_4_5_6_9"><mxCell style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontSize=11;fillColor=#eeb3b3;strokeColor=#c0392b;fontColor=#5a1410;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="577" y="717" width="200" height="108" as="geometry"/></mxCell></object><object label="Person-affecting&lt;br&gt;view&lt;br&gt;[1+2+3+4+5+6+9+10]&lt;br&gt;→ Shrimp Welfare Project&lt;br&gt;(Jan Narveson, Melinda Roberts)" tooltip="&lt;b&gt;parochial + far_away_humans + animals_somewhat + future_humans_matter_with_discounting + no_discounting_future_humans + animals_matter_a_lot + suffering_focused + living_in_simulation + person_affecting_view&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Person-affecting population ethics: making happy people is neutral, so the astronomical case for x-risk reduction — which rests on the sheer number of extra future lives saved from extinction — loses almost all its force. Only the harm to people who exist regardless still counts. This is the standard premise longtermism&#x27;s critics deny (discussed as the key objection in Greaves &amp; MacAskill&#x27;s &#x27;The Case for Strong Longtermism&#x27;). It requires no_discounting_future_humans, the astronomical-stakes move it pushes back on. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 3 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 4 no_discounting_future_humans → 5 animals_matter_a_lot → 6 suffering_focused → 9 living_in_simulation → 10 person_affecting_view" link="https://www.squiggle-langua