56" width="251" height="108" as="geometry"/></mxCell></object><object label="Count soil animals&lt;br&gt;(~10^19 nematodes)&lt;br&gt;[1+2+3+4+5+6+9+10+11]&lt;br&gt;→ Shrimp Welfare Project&lt;br&gt;(Vasco Grilo)" tooltip="&lt;b&gt;parochial + far_away_humans + animals_somewhat + future_humans_matter_with_discounting + no_discounting_future_humans + animals_matter_a_lot + suffering_focused + living_in_simulation + person_affecting_view + soil_animals&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Grilo&#x27;s soil-animal accounting: ~10^19 soil nematodes, mites and springtails dominate the welfare effects of almost anything. Global-health charities raise food demand and cropland (~137 m^2-yr/$ for GiveWell top charities, ~1.11 kQALY/$ of soil-animal welfare change); with soil lives net-negative, the arithmetic makes GiveWell&#x27;s top charities net-harmful. Only enters once invertebrates already count, so it requires animals_matter_a_lot. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 3 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 4 no_discounting_future_humans → 5 animals_matter_a_lot → 6 suffering_focused → 9 living_in_simulation → 10 person_affecting_view → 11 soil_animals" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJylVmFz4jYQ%2FSs7mXZKaEJsIATo8IEQ7i5TrndD0nY6x41P2GusRpY8khyHy%2BW%2Fd2VDAgHamymfjHb1dvft6kmPRxHGLBd2pCI86h%2BdncFgMIBbzbgEqyDU7OuSPgoJs7zp%2BW0olBbRPccCCj9oBq2gHZwHnaAX%2BF7g%2B1AzVmXg%2B8cOZyYJb2hMnmaWKwlhQrB98CBjWoUJZ8Kh%2Br0m%2BBAzHbCCLYMkT5k0a0MTmOQpEyYwKsUiYXZtaUGc21zjakOQMmtRBwW3SRBxE6pcWi4Xa%2Fc2SLW5HmztXnudP4dbwbFAqOeQHTB5HKMut6swNxitTT0Q%2FN6tcxkYnuaClRWvy6OSURslA0b7wzJ%2ByeHa7oNRXASr4CVvYxYmwF7I4wYYfFzahL5jLhCoQy9mcwbWkcOiyJyARmorl2hA6RJM4ylxzlKkmrihdZtg1Y6fDPEowxLjFwhVminjaHt2oL0yQkKkJV6lZiyTERNKIqQ0N6IBX57HYnz%2FxaXqtuNDRrXSxnsmcgQVlwgvE9QowS7RWJjnS8hdGLfR4GZhfbhJNE8z%2BBMFDQnCR63%2BJtxq99vxb%2BPp8HZ8BfMlLFCiZhYb2XI9rhhxu0VTnYwnNAu2SsYxSUgl1hXXhAtYtgiIZnQtUHpBHGWUAtNLmFOImIecvk%2Fgcvzmw3RMHGgmSoQC%2BSJx3SVGhHIHKOFfqs4JtZBKU3eh5%2