atter_with_discounting + no_discounting_future_humans + animals_matter_a_lot + suffering_focused + person_affecting_view + soil_animals&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Grilo&#x27;s soil-animal accounting: ~10^19 soil nematodes, mites and springtails dominate the welfare effects of almost anything. Global-health charities raise food demand and cropland (~137 m^2-yr/$ for GiveWell top charities, ~1.11 kQALY/$ of soil-animal welfare change); with soil lives net-negative, the arithmetic makes GiveWell&#x27;s top charities net-harmful. Only enters once invertebrates already count, so it requires animals_matter_a_lot. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 3 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 4 no_discounting_future_humans → 5 animals_matter_a_lot → 6 suffering_focused → 10 person_affecting_view → 11 soil_animals" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJylVmFz4jYQ%2FSs7mXYKNCE2EAJ0%2BEAId5cp17shaTud48Yn7DVWI0seSQ7hcvnvXdlAIEB7M%2BWT0a7e7r5dPenpJMKY5cIOVYQnvZPzc%2Bj3%2B3CnGZdgFYSafV3Sx0LCNG94fgsWSovogeMCFn7QCJpBK7gI2oHvBb4PFWNVBr5fdShTSWgDY%2FI0s1xJCBMC7YEHGdMqTDgTDtPvNsCHmOmALdgySPKUSbM2NIBJnjJhAqNSXCTMri1NiHOba1xtCFJmLepgwW0SRNyEKpeWy%2FnavQVSba8HO7vXXhebcCs4Fgi1CdkGk8cx6mK7CnOD0aYAKgq1UTJg5BEWEQqO1nYfjOIiWMEXzIxYmAB7oYcbYPBxaRP6jrlAoA68mM05WFc%2BiyJzChqpbVyiAaULMI1nxCpLkbLmhtZtgiXhPxliSoYFxi8QqjRTxhGzcaC9MkJCpCVepmYskxETSiKkNBeiDl82bR89fHGpuu34mFGttPGBiRxBxQXCy4TUC7ArNBZm%2BRJyF8ZtNLhdWA9uE83TDP5EQWOA8FGrvwm33P129NtoMrgbXcNsCXOUqJnFerZcjyNG3O7QVCPjKXXblsk4JgmpwLrmmnABixYB0YyuBUrPiaOMUmB6CTMKEfOQ0%2FcpXI3efJiMiAPNRIGwQD5PXHeJEaHcAUn4l7JzQs2l0tRd6Ho%2FwvAGKkpTvWcqPkvZXHKbRwhXH%2B5GwyrlY1Se%2FcptmKC8ZmL5EfXvJoI%2BPE0l0CipTOA7FBlGG4tX9y5cQK9%2B4XwWKMQMKZO31EIHUbp4funj%2Bc6pmHbUMQttzsQVk%2Fd%2FFJ1yrs0jkWoHoGtQ8eHsGFx1Kp%2Bnch7tFOJy8VqrZLzGVLI03nNoriryGpQu4%2Bmew7qaBtVsE7Fj9%2BsNZ21dEpuLbNfU8Dxnu2xRElO54CKa5XOz69MufTqNwocJEWN0oBeDueYhCWROMzBklhmrVZYgeQ1R0uqa%2BOYq1aI7gj%2BguWUPBavXSgimb%2BKt3eWeIv%2BG84%2FKuGMeO1PTKyIP%2BQMX%2FCtz