&gt;&lt;br&gt;Asymmetry: averting intense suffering takes priority over creating happiness. Factory farming, malaria and the worst wild-animal conditions weigh up; speculative future-flourishing bets weigh down. Arises most naturally from taking animal suffering seriously, so it requires animals_somewhat. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 3 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 4 no_discounting_future_humans → 6 suffering_focused" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJylVmFT4kgQ%2FStd1l0dcooJoJ5c8QERV2vZWwu527oSC4ekQ%2BaczKRmJkbW9b9fTwIKAp5Vly%2BEdM%2Fr7tczb%2FppJ8SIZcJ2VYg7rZ2DA2i32zDUjEuwCgLNvs%2FoJZcwyuqe34RcaRE%2BcMwh98f1cWPcHB9BxViVwtGuWzySBNIxJktSy5WEICasFniQMq2CmDPhoPyTOvgQMT1mOZuN4yxh0iwMdWCSJ0yYsVEJ5jGzC0sDosxmGucLxgmzFvU45zYeh9wEKpOWy%2BnCvQlSLX8fr6xeeB2ByaIIdeGggsxgWBTRY0EM7LUSboDB1czG9B5xgUAcvZrNAViXKQtDswcaiVgu0YDSBZjGfSKAJUj5ckPfbYwlN78YKkoGBcbvEKgkVcbV8OJAa2WIhEifuCnQjGUyZEJJhIQ6J2pw99KY3sOdS9Utx8cUA0sLH5jIEFRUILz2sFaAnaKxMMlmkLkwbqHB5cJa0LkEwyK0M6gMMMyVCmFATkwH8W6J8an3R2%2FQGfbOYDKDKUrUzGItnS22DYbcrpBVJeMetceWKTk%2BCanAOuOasgakntAPkY2uEUpPialU08bQM5hQiIgHnN734LR3%2FnXQIyY0EwVCjnwau4YTL0K5jRzzu7J%2FQk2l0rS54MT7GbqXUFGaqt5X0X7CppLbLEQ4%2FTrsdV1lRmXpZ26DGOUZE7Mr1H%2BaENrwNJIAKapU4AWKFMMXi1fzDl1Ar3bofHIUYoKUySdqpIMoXTy%2F9PF851RsT9QRC2zGxCmT938V%2FXKujS2Rqhugq1DxYX8b3O5IPo%2FkNFwpxOXiNefJePWRZEm05tCYV%2BTVKV3GkzWHRTV1qtnGYsXu1%2BrO2jwmNvN01VT3PGc7blISI5lzEU6yqVn1OSp9fqsXPkyICMMNvehMNQ9IyDLaA11mmbFapTGSVxclfV0Q35inWnRH8Ac01%2ByhYPVMCcH0ZbS0ulxT5F93%2FmEZt88jZ2p4ReQuf%2BCCf2duX%2Fdk6BpCsHINZrEvipaTBtxfx0zjABO1HN%2BVjPt%2BUTO9eCfOu5QtV7Xp2GvL7h2k770%2Bhbf35vkgL9X%2FpqG6UvmvH0P9CDHVd4iobii72MK6lKD1TfA4IDASqCxYJ7QxJ9Sv%2Fz9CN8fYmmt5kdzkZ53%2B30AMa6fGKansT7etZV0LVzTP8mR%2BQ7xqWqDISIpH%2FL5RcVrO3ty3kGbWOOnk1qlYoNzt0YYbV8ET0CHHFox2%2BiogHXQaB%2FelyI129iAPX4htQYJMVjaq4C4VTfIEz3uroK7HpYKL2Wa4ZQl6D%2BUbCRy4wYJK0txdPp0v57ubMVdky4GuQ3Yuv8ABdOdYPWk1pnSzYqZNzNMtsMtity3XIfXpwk0UCH1k0ww3Y60IY4nlH%2FrHjeYa4HVMt1wKVD8NSA