lmost all its force. Only the harm to people who exist regardless still counts. This is the standard premise longtermism&#x27;s critics deny (discussed as the key objection in Greaves &amp; MacAskill&#x27;s &#x27;The Case for Strong Longtermism&#x27;). It requires no_discounting_future_humans, the astronomical-stakes move it pushes back on. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 3 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 4 no_discounting_future_humans → 6 suffering_focused → 9 living_in_simulation → 10 person_affecting_view" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJylVmFzGjcQ%2FSs7nnaKqY3vgMQ1HT5gTBJPSJPBbjOdkLmIuz1OtU66kXQ%2BE8f%2FvSsd2GAgzUz5dGhXb3ffSm91f5BgykphhyrBg97ByQn0%2B3241oxLsApizb4u6KOSMC3bQdiFSmmR3HKsoAqjdtSJutHL6CwKA2gYqwoIg0MHMZUENTCmzAvLlYQ4I8QeBFAwreKMM%2BEAw7M2hJAyHbGKLaKszJk0K0MbmOQ5EyYyKscqY3Zl6UBa2lLjckOUM2tRRxW3WZRwE6tSWi7nK%2FcuSLW%2BHm3sXnm9BFOmKWrvoOLSYLIynYHgt26dy8jwvBTM17QqgIpCbZSMGO2PfQRHkKdgxOIM2BMP3ACDDwub0XfKBQLx%2FGQ2J2BdnSxJzBFopOZwiQaU9mAaj4k%2BliNVyw2t2wxrZn8xRImMPcbvEKu8UMYx8OhAe2WChEhL3Hg0Y5lMmFASIafuixZ8eWzu6PaLS9Vtx7uCiqKNt0yUCCr1CE%2FnoOXBztFYmJULKF0Yt9HgemE9uCasN45xhDGyeYn1xtejP0aTwfXoAmYLmKNEzSy2isXqvGHC7QZDTTIeUUdtnYcjkZA81gXXlCqgbwMQw%2BjYV3pO9BSazpJewIxCpDzm9H0E56NX7ycjKl8z4REq5PPMdZDIEMrdgIx%2FqZsm1FwqTecRzoKfYXgJDaWp1GOVHudsLrktE4Tz99ej4SHlY1RZvOU2zlBeMLH4gPpPk0Af7qcS6LioQuAbFAUmj5agFbxwAYPWC%2BdToRAzpExeU%2FccRO0ShLVPEDonf6JRpyy2JRPnTN785ZvkXDt7IjV3QDehEcLxPrjDqXyYynmyUYjLJegukwnaU8nydMuhs6woaFO6jOdbDqtq2lSzzcSGPWy1nbV7SmxWxaapHQTOdtqlJKay4iKZlXOz6fOy9vmt7X2YECkmO3oxmGsekwKWdAaGzDJjtSoyJK8hSlpdEd9Zpuq7Q3qA5ordelYvlBBMX6Zru%2Bs9Pv%2B280%2FquGOeOlMn8JGHJCqCf%2FViMpKJawjByi2Y1bnwLaeLf3OVMY0TzNV6fFcyHoe%2BZvoIzpx3rXSuajOwV5bdOMgwePp57%2BDZ7wd5af43Dc2Nyn%2F9MdQfIab5HSKaO8r2R5jkr1JqxyG4mxDYBJMy3ia0syQ0bP8%2FQnfH2JtrPT0%2BVReD8d9ADGsnwTRn4KfPvXVdSzY0z%2FJ8ORaeNC1WZCTFI36fSTdtZ89GNBSlNU46uXUqFis3MvrwyVVwD3TJsQfTg7GKSQedxsFNLXLTgyOokkdie5Ajk42dKnhIRZM8wcPRJqjrca3gYrEbbl2CvofykQQO3GOEStLc