 living_in_simulation&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;If most observers like us are simulated, the astronomical future that justified x-risk work probably gets switched off long before it happens. The same expected-value reasoning that bought astronomical stakes now attenuates them: future-facing value is multiplied by the probability the simulation keeps running, and the ranking slides back toward the present. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 3 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 4 no_discounting_future_humans → 9 living_in_simulation" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJylVmFz4jYQ%2FSs7TDsFSoiBpDno8IEAuWTK9TJJ2ptOyHDCXmM1suSR5DhcLv%2B9KxsSCKbNTP0F41293X0rPe1TJcCQpcIOVYCVXuXwEPr9PtxoxiVYBb5m35b0kkmYpm2vdQSZ0iJ44JhB1pq1Z53Z0awLVWNVAt2aWzyVBDIwJo0Ty5UEPyKsHniQMK38iDPhoFrdNrQgZHrGMracRWnMpFkb2sAkj5kwM6NizCJm15YOhKlNNa4WzGJmLepZxm00C7jxVSotl4u1%2BxFItfl9trV67dUFwR%2BclcuZ4XEqmEs8r2PM%2FAjYazHcAIPLpY3oPeQCgWh6NZtDsC5ZFgSmARqJWy7RgNI5mMYD4oDFSClzQ99thAU9PxmqS%2Fo5xq%2FgqzhRxpXx4kBrZYCESJ%2B4ydGMZTJgQkmEmJonmvD1pTfjh68uVbccHxP0LS18YCJFUGGO8NrGZg52isbCPF1C6sK4hQY3C%2BvB4AIMC9EuoXqFQaZUAFfkxLQf1QqMj%2BPfx1eDm%2FEI5ktYoETNLDaT5XrnYMDtFll1MjaoQ7ZIyfFJSDnWiGvKGjAM3Q%2BRja4RSi%2BIqUTT3tBLmFOIkPuc3htwOj77fDUmJjQTOUKGfBG5nhMvQrm9HPGvRf%2BEWkilaX9B1%2FsRhhdQVZqqPlDhQcwWkts0QDj9fDMeusqMSpPfuPUjlCMmlpeo%2FzAB9OFpKgESVInAcxQJBi8Wr%2Bkdu4Be89j5ZCjEHCmTj9RIB1G4eK3Cx2s5p3yHog6Zb1MmTpm8%2FzPvl3Pt7IlUL4GuQ7UFB%2FvgalP5PJWLYKsQl4t3tErGa08li8Mdh86qIq9N6TIe7zisq2lTzTYSW%2FZWs%2B2sRyfEZpZsm9qe52wnR5TEVGZcBPN0YbZ9fil8PrRzHyZEiEFJLwYLzX3SspT2wJBZZqxWSYTkNURJX9fEd1ap5t2ho4%2Fmmj3krI6UEExfhBurizV5%2Fm3nHxRxJzx0po6XRx6Sfgj%2BLdeNsQxcQwhW7sCs90XectKA%2B%2BuIabzCWG3GdyXjQSuvmV68rvMulMtVbQb22rJ7B9nyXp%2Fc23vzvJOX%2Bn%2FTUN%2Bq%2FOf3ob6HmPq%2FEFEvKTvfwrqQoN1N8HhFYCRQqb9LaGdFaKv9%2Fwgtj7E31%2BIiuc1Gg8lfQAxrp8YJqewPd71NXQu2NM%2FyeHVDvGqar8hIikf8vlFxWs7eXLmQpNY46eTWqZiv3O3Rh1tXwRPQIcceTCsT5ZMOOo2D%2B0LkppUGZMELsT2IkclqqQrWqOgWPDe2IV2HC%2F0Wy3KwTQHaj%